<br>
IMO, the criteria that should be used in judging if classes overlap too much is if there are any classes that basically play the same.  ie, Paladins and Shadowknights play pretty similarily meleeing with the same type of weapons, tanking, and using spells to hold taunt and affect combat.<br>
